<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .showcase-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem; 
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            width: 30%; 
            min-width: 280px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #38bdf8;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .product-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .product-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #38bdf8;
        }

        .product-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.5;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .buy-btn {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #38bdf8;
            color: #0f172a;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .buy-btn:hover {
            background-color: #7dd3fc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="showcase-container">
        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a, #3b82f6);">[PLACA DE VÍDEO]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">RTX 4070 SUPER</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">Performance incrível em 1440p com tecnologias DLSS 3.5 e Ray Tracing avançado.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #581c87, #a855f7);">[PROCESSADOR]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">Ryzen 7 7800X3D</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">O rei do gaming. Tecnologia 3D V-Cache para taxas de quadros incomparáveis.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #064e3b, #10b981);">[MEMÓRIA RAM]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">32GB DDR5 6000MHz</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">Alta velocidade e baixa latência para multitarefas pesadas e edição de vídeo.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c2d12, #f97316);">[PLACA MÃE]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">B650M AM5 Wi-Fi</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">Robusta, com dissipadores de calor premium e suporte para as tecnologias mais recentes.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #312e81, #6366f1);">[MONITOR]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">Monitor 144Hz IPS</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">Cores vibrantes e tempo de resposta de 1ms para uma jogabilidade fluida e precisa.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #451a03, #d97706);">[FONTE]</div>
            <h2 class="product-title">Fonte 850W Gold</h2>
            <p class="product-desc">Eficiência energética garantida e cabos totalmente modulares para um setup limpo.</p>
            <button class="buy-btn">Ver Preço</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
